FAQs

Here are frequently asked questions to clear all your doubts
Still have doubts?
Talk to our representative
How do I schedule a mock interview?
Step 1: Go to intervue.io/mock-interviews
Step 2: Select the profile and rounds suitable to your evaluation requirements
Step 3: Add candidate and company details and click 'Schedule Interview'
What kind of questions can I expect?
Our interviews concentrate on the core principles of computer science, data structures, algorithms, and systems design. The questions will closely align in subject matter and difficulty to those typically encountered in technical interviews for backend or full-stack roles at leading companies
How much do mock interviews cost?
The mock interviews costs between the range of Rs. 1200-2300, based on the type of interviewer you select
I want to be an interviewer. What do I need to do?
You can sign-up as an interviewer by visiting intervue.io/become-an-interview-engineer and we'll get back to you ASAP
